 | format =
 | doi =
 | accessdate =2007-10-30}}</ref> He also led unsuccessful protests to change the school name to [[Malcolm X]] High.<ref name="naacp"/> After attaining his [[GED]], for a number of semesters he studied at [[Goddard College]] in rural [[Vermont]].<ref name="tsb">{{cite news 
 | last =Burroughs
 | first =Todd Steven 
