Several others made statements that supported Abu-Jamal's case. William Singletary has stated that he directly witnessed the entire incident and that he would be willing to testify that Abu-Jamal was not the gunman.<ref>{{cite news 
 | last ="Minister of Information JR" 
 | first =
 | coauthors =
 | title =William Singletary, eyewitness on the night Mumia was shot and framed - Part 2
 | work =
 | pages =
