Court stenographer Terri Maurer-Carter stated in an affidavit of August 2001 that in the presence of herself and two others the presiding Judge had exclaimed, "Yeah, and I'm going to help them fry the nigger",<ref>{{cite web
 | last =
 | first =
 | authorlink =
 | coauthors =
 | title =Statement of Terri Maurer-Carter
 | work =
 | publisher =Labournet UK
 | date =[[August 21]], [[2001]] 
 | url =http://www.labournet.net/mumia/0109/terrimc.html
