 | accessdate =2007-10-31}}</ref>, and [[Montreal]]<ref name = "humanite"/> have also conferred their citizenship upon him. 
* In 2001 he received the biannual [[Erich Mühsam]] Prize of the Erich Mühsam Society, [[Lübeck]], awarded to "individuals and groups that deal with moral courage and idealism for social justice and persecuted minorities".<ref>{{cite news 
